{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1723,"text":"Please meet Jane."},{"time":3644,"text":"She has a high-risk pregnancy."},{"time":5663,"text":"Within 24 weeks,"},{"time":7444,"text":"she's on bed rest at the hospital,"},{"time":9629,"text":"being monitored\nfor her preterm contractions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13024,"text":"She doesn't look the happiest."},{"time":14942,"text":"That's in part because it requires\ntechnicians and experts"},{"time":18187,"text":"to apply these clunky belts on her\nto monitor her uterine contractions."},{"time":23550,"text":"Another reason Jane is not so happy\nis because she's worried."},{"time":28768,"text":"In particular, she's worried\nabout what happens"},{"time":31418,"text":"after her 10-day stay\non bed rest at the hospital."},{"time":35438,"text":"What happens when she's home?"},{"time":37532,"text":"If she were to give birth this early\nit would be devastating."},{"time":41874,"text":"As an African-American woman,"},{"time":43652,"text":"she's twice as likely\nto have a premature birth"},{"time":47376,"text":"or to have a stillbirth."},{"time":49551,"text":"So Jane basically has one of two options:"},{"time":52553,"text":"stay at the hospital on bed rest,"},{"time":55237,"text":"a prisoner to the technology\nuntil she gives birth,"},{"time":59469,"text":"and then spend the rest\nof her life paying for the bill;"},{"time":62946,"text":"or head home after her 10-day stay\nand hope for the best."},{"time":68198,"text":"Neither of these two options\nseems appealing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72132,"text":"As I began to think\nabout stories like this"},{"time":74267,"text":"and hear about stories like this,"},{"time":76077,"text":"I began to ask myself and imagine:"},{"time":78194,"text":"Is there an alternative?"},{"time":79760,"text":"Is there a way we could have\nthe benefits of high-fidelity monitoring"},{"time":84520,"text":"that we get with our trusted\npartners in the hospital"},{"time":87343,"text":"while someone is at home\nliving their daily life?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":90832,"text":"With that in mind,"},{"time":92351,"text":"I encouraged people in my research group"},{"time":94322,"text":"to partner with some\nclever material scientists,"},{"time":97854,"text":"and all of us came together\nand brainstormed."},{"time":100904,"text":"And after a long process,"},{"time":102369,"text":"we came up with a vision, an idea,"},{"time":104787,"text":"of a wearable system that perhaps\nyou could wear like a piece of jewelry"},{"time":108589,"text":"or you could apply\nto yourself like a Band-Aid."},{"time":111463,"text":"And after many trials and tribulations\nand years of endeavors,"},{"time":115670,"text":"we were able to come up\nwith this flexible electronic patch"},{"time":119421,"text":"that was manufactured\nusing the same processes"},{"time":121840,"text":"that they use to build computer chips,"},{"time":124545,"text":"except the electronics are transferred\nfrom a semiconductor wafer"},{"time":129001,"text":"onto a flexible material\nthat can interface with the human body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133775,"text":"These systems are about\nthe thickness of a human hair."},{"time":138006,"text":"They can measure the types\nof information that we want,"},{"time":141948,"text":"things such as:"},{"time":143151,"text":"bodily movement,"},{"time":144670,"text":"bodily temperature,"},{"time":146098,"text":"electrical rhythms of the body"},{"time":147927,"text":"and so forth."},{"time":149403,"text":"We can also engineer these systems,"},{"time":151883,"text":"so they can integrate energy sources,"},{"time":154877,"text":"and can have wireless\ntransmission capabilities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158624,"text":"So as we began to build\nthese types of systems,"},{"time":162553,"text":"we began to test them on ourselves\nin our research group."},{"time":166915,"text":"But in addition, we began to reach out\nto some of our clinical partners"},{"time":170303,"text":"in San Diego,"},{"time":171482,"text":"and test these on different patients\nin different clinical conditions,"},{"time":175206,"text":"including moms-to-be like Jane."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178531,"text":"Here is a picture of a pregnant woman\nin labor at our university hospital"},{"time":183535,"text":"being monitored for her uterine\ncontractions with the conventional belt."},{"time":188939,"text":"In addition,"},{"time":190114,"text":"our flexible electronic patches are there."},{"time":193268,"text":"This picture demonstrates waveforms\npertaining to the fetal heart rate,"},{"time":197568,"text":"where the red corresponds\nto what was acquired"},{"time":200509,"text":"with the conventional belts,"},{"time":202112,"text":"and the blue corresponds to our estimates"},{"time":204794,"text":"using our flexible electronic systems\nand our algorithms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208932,"text":"At this moment,"},{"time":210404,"text":"we gave ourselves a big mental high five."},{"time":213508,"text":"Some of the things we had imagined\nwere beginning to come to fruition,"},{"time":216939,"text":"and we were actually seeing this\nin a clinical context."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220083,"text":"But there was still a problem."},{"time":221974,"text":"The problem was, the way\nwe manufactured these systems"},{"time":225359,"text":"was very inefficient,"},{"time":226840,"text":"had low yield"},{"time":228021,"text":"and was very error-prone."},{"time":230105,"text":"In addition,"},{"time":231280,"text":"as we talked to some\nof the nurses in the hospital,"},{"time":233776,"text":"they encouraged us to make sure"},{"time":235990,"text":"that our electronics worked\nwith typical medical adhesives"},{"time":240027,"text":"that are used in a hospital."},{"time":242217,"text":"We had an epiphany and said,\n\"Wait a minute."},{"time":244998,"text":"Rather than just making\nthem work with adhesives,"},{"time":247693,"text":"let's integrate them into adhesives,"},{"time":251194,"text":"and that could solve\nour manufacturing problem.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":254269,"text":"This picture that you see here"},{"time":256284,"text":"is our ability to embed these censors\ninside of a piece of Scotch tape"},{"time":260803,"text":"by simply peeling it off of a wafer."},{"time":264255,"text":"Ongoing work in our research group\nallows us to, in addition,"},{"time":267648,"text":"embed integrated circuits\ninto the flexible adhesives"},{"time":271381,"text":"to do things like amplifying signals\nand digitizing them,"},{"time":275095,"text":"processing them"},{"time":276297,"text":"and encoding for wireless transmission."},{"time":279113,"text":"All of this integrated\ninto the same medical adhesives"},{"time":283039,"text":"that are used in the hospital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285810,"text":"So when we reached this point,"},{"time":287326,"text":"we had some other challenges,"},{"time":289774,"text":"from both an engineering\nas well as a usability perspective,"},{"time":293113,"text":"to make sure that we could\nmake it used practically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297207,"text":"In many digital health discussions,"},{"time":299718,"text":"people believe in and embrace the idea\nthat we can simply digitize the data,"},{"time":304689,"text":"wirelessly transmit it,"},{"time":306293,"text":"send it to the cloud,"},{"time":307791,"text":"and in the cloud,"},{"time":309012,"text":"we can extract meaningful\ninformation for interpretation."},{"time":312147,"text":"And indeed, you can do all of that,"},{"time":314648,"text":"if you're not worried\nabout some of the energy challenges."},{"time":317661,"text":"Think about Jane for a moment."},{"time":319348,"text":"She doesn't live in Palo Alto,"},{"time":321176,"text":"nor does she live in Beverly Hills."},{"time":323359,"text":"What that means is,"},{"time":324541,"text":"we have to be mindful about her data plan\nand how much it would cost"},{"time":327895,"text":"for her to be sending out\na continuous stream of data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332383,"text":"There's another challenge"},{"time":333686,"text":"that not everyone in the medical\nprofession is comfortable talking about."},{"time":337408,"text":"And that is, that Jane\ndoes not have the most trust"},{"time":340260,"text":"in the medical establishment."},{"time":342460,"text":"She, people like her, her ancestors,\nhave not had the best experiences"},{"time":347623,"text":"at the hands of doctors and the hospital"},{"time":351163,"text":"or insurance companies."},{"time":353466,"text":"That means that we have to be mindful\nof questions of privacy."},{"time":356831,"text":"Jane might not feel that happy"},{"time":358476,"text":"about all that data\nbeing processed into the cloud."},{"time":362712,"text":"And Jane cannot be fooled;"},{"time":365346,"text":"she reads the news."},{"time":366854,"text":"She knows that if the federal\ngovernment can be hacked,"},{"time":369848,"text":"if the Fortune 500 can be hacked,"},{"time":372409,"text":"so can her doctor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375014,"text":"And so with that in mind,"},{"time":376773,"text":"we had an epiphany."},{"time":378858,"text":"We cannot outsmart\nall the hackers in the world,"},{"time":381612,"text":"but perhaps we can present\nthem a smaller target."},{"time":384986,"text":"What if we could actually,"},{"time":387191,"text":"rather than have those algorithms\nthat do data interpretation"},{"time":391147,"text":"run in the cloud,"},{"time":392904,"text":"what if we have those algorithms run\non those small integrated circuits"},{"time":396339,"text":"embedded into those adhesives?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":398995,"text":"And so when we integrate\nthese things together,"},{"time":402113,"text":"what this means is that now\nwe can think about the future"},{"time":405641,"text":"where someone like Jane can still\ngo about living her normal daily life,"},{"time":409730,"text":"she can be monitored,"},{"time":411226,"text":"it can be done in a way where\nshe doesn't have to get another job"},{"time":414750,"text":"to pay her data plan,"},{"time":416239,"text":"and we can also address\nsome of her concerns about privacy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420907,"text":"So at this point,"},{"time":422081,"text":"we're feeling very good about ourselves."},{"time":424109,"text":"We've accomplished this,"},{"time":425296,"text":"we've begun to address some\nof these questions about privacy"},{"time":428490,"text":"and we feel like, pretty much\nthe chapter is closed now."},{"time":432405,"text":"Everyone lived happily ever after, right?"},{"time":436751,"text":"Well, not so fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438338,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":439567,"text":"One of the things we have to remember,\nas I mentioned earlier,"},{"time":442631,"text":"is that Jane does not have the most trust\nin the medical establishment."},{"time":446036,"text":"We have to remember"},{"time":447223,"text":"that there are increasing\nand widening health disparities,"},{"time":450761,"text":"and there's inequity in terms\nof proper care management."},{"time":454616,"text":"And so what that means\nis that this simple picture"},{"time":457134,"text":"of Jane and her data --"},{"time":458803,"text":"even with her being comfortable\nbeing wirelessly transmitted to the cloud,"},{"time":462754,"text":"letting a doctor intervene if necessary --"},{"time":465093,"text":"is not the whole story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467091,"text":"So what we're beginning to do"},{"time":468509,"text":"is to think about ways to have\ntrusted parties serve as intermediaries"},{"time":473360,"text":"between people like Jane\nand her health care providers."},{"time":476802,"text":"For example, we've begun\nto partner with churches"},{"time":479837,"text":"and to think about nurses\nthat are church members,"},{"time":482718,"text":"that come from that trusted community,"},{"time":484764,"text":"as patient advocates and health coaches\nto people like Jane."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489462,"text":"Another thing we have going for us"},{"time":491493,"text":"is that insurance companies, increasingly,"},{"time":493553,"text":"are attracted to some of these ideas."},{"time":495906,"text":"They're increasingly realizing"},{"time":497637,"text":"that perhaps it's better\nto pay one dollar now"},{"time":500601,"text":"for a wearable device and a health coach,"},{"time":503608,"text":"rather than paying 10 dollars later,"},{"time":506253,"text":"when that baby is born prematurely"},{"time":508831,"text":"and ends up in the neonatal\nintensive care unit --"},{"time":511796,"text":"one of the most expensive\nparts of a hospital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515697,"text":"This has been a long\nlearning process for us."},{"time":518593,"text":"This iterative process of breaking\nthrough and attacking one problem"},{"time":522452,"text":"and not feeling totally comfortable,"},{"time":524247,"text":"and identifying the next problem,"},{"time":526090,"text":"has helped us go along this path"},{"time":528171,"text":"of actually trying to not only\ninnovate with this technology"},{"time":531271,"text":"but make sure it can be used for people\nwho perhaps need it the most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535709,"text":"Another learning lesson\nwe've taken from this process"},{"time":538517,"text":"that is very humbling,"},{"time":539920,"text":"is that as technology progresses\nand advances at an accelerating rate,"},{"time":544271,"text":"we have to remember that human beings\nare using this technology,"},{"time":548237,"text":"and we have to be mindful"},{"time":549863,"text":"that these human beings --\nthey have a face,"},{"time":553327,"text":"they have a name"},{"time":554613,"text":"and a life."},{"time":555798,"text":"And in the case of Jane,"},{"time":557433,"text":"hopefully, two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560041,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561259,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}